Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure he's here on the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tsumugu hasn't been in the sea at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet he somehow got cursed with that fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}'s gotta be somewhere in Oshiooshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But where would he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, it's not like he's a lost dog or cat or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, this is so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is this really gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.16,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure we can catch him with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We found this porn mag on the shore, \Nso we're laying a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} likes perverted things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I also brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ooh!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You made that for {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has bamboo shoots, carrots, and chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared them all separately and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma's is still much better, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy it turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it gets {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You all keep treating him like he's a lost pet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he {\i1}does{\i0} eat stuff \Neven after it falls on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what if he even has super-hairy knuckles and is a total lech?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have hairy knuckles, \Nbut he has scales on his chest and his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, I guess they don't call him a "scale" for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you had something to tell me \Nafter the Boatdrift Ceremony.{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me now.{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it you were gonna say?{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it about Tsumugu?{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Tsumugu, isn't it?!{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring off into space for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lately, more and more saltflake snow has been falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and according to the news,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's even falling in towns and cities far from the sea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't just search aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there somewhere on the surface that's connected to the sea god?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Can you think of a place like that, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I think there's an old shrine somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going back to campus soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you have time to help out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's just south of the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it's sort of run-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} is also part of our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait, you sure that place is related to the sea god, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds just like a fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours did too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you got one on your knee, \Nyou totally hated it.{Yep, took a fish to the knee.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go feed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Feed it? It {\i1}eats{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Wanna come watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go make us some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's snowing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} ate some of the stew I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so you were once cursed with a fish too, Manaka{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I was totally surprised, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it disappeared, \Nyou lied and said it was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It eats kinda like a frog! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient gave me those bean pastries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Was it a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. It was an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try asking you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before long,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mihashi{-sensei} had to head back to campus unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With all the snow, his research here was delayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and since the weather was getting dangerous, \Nhe was called back to his lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about leaving suddenly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is from Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She said to eat it on your way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I tried to tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This weather is exactly why I should stay {\i1}here{\i0}. \NThey wouldn't listen, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the saltflake snow everywhere really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you remember hearing it on the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting heavy snow \Neven further inland now,{Note: You would think that "inland" would be a distance thing (needing "farther"), but based on search results, I suppose it's a "degree/level of how inland a place is" sort of thing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's been causing power outages and problems with traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going back with him, Tsumugu{-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I'm staying here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well... there's still \Nsome daylight to burn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna go look for that Uroko bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu, let's go help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you staying longer because of Chisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was sure you'd say you're staying because of your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want an answer too.
