Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't Hikari and Manaka{-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,seem a little off to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Shiodome. What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's going to snow again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably safer for you to go home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Thank you.
