Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Minegishi asked you out, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you bringing that up {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked you out, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}, Hii{-kun}! Look! The food and the porn magazine are both gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know that for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It coulda been some random old perv, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it was definitely {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He really {\i1}is{\i0} on the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's not here either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When Tsumugu and I raced...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up and got myself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, you were the first one to dive in after me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember that either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What else don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even remember the fish curse on your knee—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I actually do remember that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember lying about it{'s} still being there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything because \NI didn't want anyone to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you know, I remember making the Wooden Maiden with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just because I'm still a little sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The day they told us we couldn't go to the surface anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}The day I couldn't help but hold you close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,when we went to Namiji Middle High before everyone fell asleep and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said I loved you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of that!{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't remember any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, you octopus{?}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you just knock over a lady and leave her there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, get the hell away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
